description:
Changed the Instruments to sound closer to the original. 

There's still more work to be done on this however, since some parts of the guitar solo should be a sawtooth, while other parts are harmonized with it. The main synths should also be chords, because they sound much thinner than they should be compared to the original. 

At least this should a good starting point for someone else to take over and make a more accurate version with the above notes in mind.
title: Turbo Killer
